FAQs
----

##### Can I extend the trial period?

If you couldn’t spend time on Rocketlane during your 14-day trial for any reason, please drop us a note at [care@rocketlane.com](mailto:care@rocketlane.com) or via our support chat with your information. We will verify your usage and extend your trial by an additional week to help with your evaluation.

##### Is implementation and onboarding assistance included in all plans?

Implementation packages are not directly included in the plans and will be charged extra based on the scope and onboarding services required. [Book a call](https://www.rocketlane.com/demo) with our Sales team to understand which package would be perfect to set you up for success.

##### Do you assist with migration from other tools?

Yes, we do! We've successfully executed 100+ migrations for clients from various project management and collaboration tools, including Mavenlink (Kantata), GuideCX, Certinia, Monday.com, Asana, and Smartsheets. Our dedicated team ensures a seamless, end-to-end migration process, typically completed within 30 days.

##### Do you have 24/7 support?

Yes! Every customer can reach us anytime via email and chat. You have real-time support right from the product. Additionally, you have access to [Rocketlane Academy](https://academy.rocketlane.com/), where you can learn about the entire platform, and our [Help Center](https://help.rocketlane.com/support/home), which is an extensive product and API library that covers the entire breadth of Rocketlane.  
‍  
On top of this, you can also opt for a premium support offering to get personalized support with a TAM, monthly ticket reviews, and holistic issue resolution.

### Move your service delivery into the fast lane  

Deliver projects on time and on budget. Collaborate with your team, partners, and customers. Without scope creep, stress, or missed goals.
